query:
with moved_task as (
                update underway.task
                set task_queue_name = $2
                where id = $1
                  and task_queue_name = $3
                returning id
            ),
            moved_attempts as (
                update underway.task_attempt
                set task_queue_name = $2
                where task_id = $1
                  and task_queue_name = $3
            )
            select exists(select 1 from moved_task) as "moved!"
